#### POST /users

Creates a new user.

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": 2,
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "email": "jane@example.com"
  }
}
```
